[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0954","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0954.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0639","title":"Unix/Linux chargen 服务未授权访问漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0639 涉及 Unix 系统上运行的多个网络服务存在远程安全漏洞。其中 chargen（字符生成）服务在目标主机上处于开启状态，该服务属于经典的\"无用服务\"，会在收到连接后持续返回随机字符流。攻击者可通过向目标主机的 chargen 端口（TCP/UDP 19）建立连接，诱导其产生大量无意义流量，并可结合 echo 等服务发起反射放大攻击，消耗系统资源或参与分布式拒绝服务（DDoS）。影响范围为默认开启或暴露此类老旧服务的 Unix/Linux 系统。利用条件为攻击者能够网络可达目标主机的 chargen 端口，且服务未做访问限制。建议关闭并禁用 chargen 等不必要的网络服务以减小攻击面。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0639"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:46.383","remediation":"在 inetd/xinetd 配置中注释掉 chargen 服务条目（如 /etc/inetd.conf 中 #chargen 及 /etc/xinetd.d/chargen 设置 disable = yes），执行 kill -HUP $(pidof inetd) 或重启 xinetd 使配置生效；同时在边界防火墙阻断 TCP/UDP 19 端口，禁止外部访问该服务以消除反射放大与信息泄露风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0639","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/1999/CVE-1999-0639.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/84f82928c38b4d0e02149dbde07f5affc7f46f43/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0639.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0639","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cc528fa33408da88ea19cf3d01d2185cd0ffe95a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0639.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0639.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1ef90eac7bb1a353721fe038daf41872bdff01c4/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gccm-p8cf-fqwm/GHSA-gccm-p8cf-fqwm.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0639.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83127/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0954.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0952","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0952.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0638","title":"Unix Daytime 服务暴露漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0638 涉及 Unix 系统上运行的多个网络服务存在远程安全漏洞。其中 daytime 服务（端口 13）在目标主机上处于开启状态，该服务会响应 TCP/UDP 请求并返回当前系统时间字符串。攻击条件为攻击者能够与暴露该服务的目标主机建立网络连接，利用方式是通过向 daytime 服务发送探测请求以确认服务存活并收集目标系统信息，从而辅助后续侦察与攻击。该漏洞本身危害较低，主要影响运行了不必要网络服务的 Unix 系统，暴露了多余的服务端口，增加了攻击面。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0638"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:46.270","remediation":"在 inetd/xinetd 配置中注释掉 daytime 服务条目（如 /etc/inetd.conf 中的 daytime stream tcp nowait 行并执行 kill -HUP 重启 inetd），或使用防火墙规则（如 iptables -A INPUT -p tcp --dport 13 -j DROP）屏蔽 TCP/UDP 13 端口，关闭不必要的 daytime 服务以减小信息泄露与攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0638","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/84f82928c38b4d0e02149dbde07f5affc7f46f43/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0638.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0638","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0638.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cc528fa33408da88ea19cf3d01d2185cd0ffe95a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0638.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1ef90eac7bb1a353721fe038daf41872bdff01c4/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vpq5-qv66-5v8c/GHSA-vpq5-qv66-5v8c.json","https://github.com/scipag/AttackToolKit/blob/78bf88564956b8f18a37659dc3d345093e95a136/plugins/Daytime%20service%20tcp%20detection.plugin","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0638.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83127/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0952.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0950","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0950.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0637","title":"Unix systat 服务 多个远程安全漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0637 指 Unix 系统上开启的 systat 远程服务存在信息泄露类安全漏洞。systat 服务（通常监听 TCP 11 端口）会在收到连接请求时返回系统当前进程状态、CPU 与内存占用等敏感信息，且默认无需任何身份认证即可访问。远程攻击者只需与目标主机建立 TCP 连接并发送请求，即可在未授权情况下获取主机运行状态与进程清单，进而辅助侦察与进一步攻击。该漏洞影响默认启用 systat 服务的各类 Unix/Linux 系统，利用条件仅为网络可达且服务端口开放，危害虽不直接导致代码执行，但显著增加了系统被探测与定向攻击的风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0637"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:46.140","remediation":"建议在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释或删除 systat 服务所在行（通常为 systat stream tcp nowait root /usr/sbin/systat），然后重启 inetd 或 xinetd 服务使配置生效。如使用 systemd 系统，执行 systemctl disable systat 并停止对应服务。作为替代监控方案，可使用 netstat、ss 等本地命令查看系统状态。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0637","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0637.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1ef693821096ed2e21366dae590c013e3dc540aa/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0637.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0637","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cc528fa33408da88ea19cf3d01d2185cd0ffe95a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0637.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0637.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1ef90eac7bb1a353721fe038daf41872bdff01c4/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8m5f-mgpp-868h/GHSA-8m5f-mgpp-868h.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0637.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83127/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0950.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0948","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0948.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0636","title":"Microsoft Windows Discard 服务权限提升漏洞","description":"目标系统上运行着不必要的 discard 网络服务（TCP/UDP 9 端口），该服务依据 RFC 863 定义仅接收并丢弃所有传入数据，本身不具备实际业务功能。该漏洞影响运行 inetd 或 xinetd 的类 Unix/Linux 系统，以及任何意外开放 9 端口的网络设备。攻击条件为攻击者能够通过网络访问目标主机的 9 端口且该服务处于监听状态。攻击者可利用该开放服务进行网络侦察以确认主机存活及服务运行状态，或在分布式拒绝服务攻击中将其作为 UDP 反射放大节点；当该服务以 root 等高权限运行时，还可被与其他漏洞链式利用，从而实现权限提升。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0636"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:46.037","remediation":"在 Windows NT/2000 中通过「控制面板→服务」停止并禁用 Discard（丢弃）服务，将其启动类型设为「已禁用」；同时在边界防火墙和主机 IPsec 策略上屏蔽 TCP/UDP 9 端口的入站流量，仅允许受信任内网访问以缓解暴露风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0636","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1ef693821096ed2e21366dae590c013e3dc540aa/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0636.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0636","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0636.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cc528fa33408da88ea19cf3d01d2185cd0ffe95a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0636.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1ef90eac7bb1a353721fe038daf41872bdff01c4/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q8p3-cw6v-69j8/GHSA-q8p3-cw6v-69j8.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0636.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/entrysky/mageni/blob/c58dcc9bc43b7fb267bb10a8083ada356fbc81d1/plugins/2020/postel/gb_discard_useless_service.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0948.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0946","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0946.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0635","title":"通用网络系统 回声服务 未授权服务运行安全漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0635 指目标系统启用了 TCP/UDP 7 号端口的回声（echo）服务。该服务会原样回显接收到的任意数据，属于多余且危险的网络服务。攻击者在无需身份认证的情况下，即可向该端口发送数据触发回显，进而可用于反射放大攻击或探测网络拓扑。其影响范围为所有默认开启 echo 服务的主机（如部分老旧 Unix/Linux 及 Windows 系统），增大了被拒绝服务攻击利用的风险。修复方式为禁用或关闭系统的 echo 服务。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0635"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:45.917","remediation":"在 /etc/inetd.conf 或 xinetd.d/echo 配置文件中注释或删除 echo 服务（端口 7/tcp 和 7/udp）条目，执行 systemctl restart inetd 或 systemctl restart xinetd 使配置生效。若系统使用 systemd，可直接执行 systemctl disable --now echo.service 禁用并停止该服务。如无法立即禁用服务，可通过防火墙规则（iptables -A INPUT -p tcp --dport 7 -j DROP）封禁端口 7 的外部访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://lists.grok.org.uk/pipermail/full-disclosure/2006-January/041434.html","http://secunia.com/advisories/18514","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0635.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1ef693821096ed2e21366dae590c013e3dc540aa/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0635.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0635","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cc528fa33408da88ea19cf3d01d2185cd0ffe95a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0635.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0635.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/echo.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1ef90eac7bb1a353721fe038daf41872bdff01c4/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wghh-7w72-v3r8/GHSA-wghh-7w72-v3r8.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0635.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83127/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0946.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0945","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0945.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0634","title":"SSH 服务运行配置暴露","description":"CVE-1999-0634 已被拒绝使用。该编号原用于描述\"SSH 服务正在运行\"这一配置状态，但经评估该条目并非直接引入安全漏洞的缺陷，而属于安全配置管理范畴。此类配置项更适合纳入通用配置枚举（CCE）体系进行管理，因此 CVE 编号委员会决定拒绝此编号。该问题不涉及具体的攻击方法、漏洞原理或影响范围。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0634"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.870","remediation":"评估 SSH 服务是否必需，非必需则关闭 sshd 服务（systemctl disable sshd）；如需保留，配置密钥认证登录、禁用 root 直接登录（PermitRootLogin no）、修改默认端口 22 为高编号端口、限制来源 IP（hosts.allow/iptables），并保持 OpenSSH 为最新稳定版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0634.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0634","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0634.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0634.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/lymwhen/lymwhen.github.io/blob/b77540924df6be1e7c614e34dd724374affd2cbf/Linux/%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D.md","https://github.com/athiasjerome/XORCISM/blob/327e2a3be196660f82c89ae9d7c4e7abe4785b0d/SOURCES/XProviderQualys/QualysSampleResults.xml","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/5c36feecacaa0eef96caef76eb433e2bf57c7235/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0634.json","https://github.com/thoraf20/vulnscan/blob/600477d061ab5462099630f9f0924cc5383c5452/network.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0945.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0943","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0943.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0633","title":"HTTP/WWW 服务运行配置检查项（非漏洞）","description":"CVE-1999-0633 已被官方驳回（REJECT），原候选编号指向\"HTTP/WWW 服务正在运行\"这一配置检测项。该条目涉及的是系统上 HTTP 服务端口的开放状态识别，并非安全漏洞，不具备攻击条件和利用方式，不产生 CVSS 评分。此类配置检查更适合归入通用配置枚举（CCE）体系，而非 CVE 漏洞编号体系。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0633"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.750","remediation":"若 HTTP 服务非业务必需，应在系统服务管理器中禁用 httpd/nginx/IIS 等相关服务并配置防火墙阻止 80/443 端口入站流量；若为业务必要，应确保移除默认页面、禁用目录列表、限制访问来源 IP、启用 TLS 并定期更新 Web 服务器至最新稳定版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0633.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0633","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0633.json","https://github.com/scipag/AttackToolKit/blob/78bf88564956b8f18a37659dc3d345093e95a136/plugins/HTTP%20index.html%20check.plugin","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0633.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000461.txt","https://github.com/lymwhen/lymwhen.github.io/blob/b77540924df6be1e7c614e34dd724374affd2cbf/Linux/%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D.md","https://github.com/Planet-Source-Code/marc-ruef-attack-tool-kit-4-0__1-58262/blob/47bd1012c1edf591e9c9fe874122b617137e1b87/atk-4.0src/plugins/HTTP%20404%20enumeration.plugin","https://github.com/zmerry/z-marvel.github.io/blob/581a79f0e7ceb8cdb3e444922154e004cca44bbb/vulbox/webvul/low/%E5%8F%AF%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87HTTP%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E8%BF%9C%E7%AB%AFWWW%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0943.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0939","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0939.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0632","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9107,\"outputTokens\":20,\"totalTokens\":10791}}","description":"RPC portmapper 服务运行在目标系统的 111/TCP 和 111/UDP 端口上，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向该服务发送请求，枚举目标主机上注册的所有 RPC 程序及其对应的端口号、版本号等信息。该漏洞可导致敏感信息泄露，攻击者可利用收集到的 RPC 服务信息进一步定位其他高危服务（如 NFS、NIS 等）并实施针对性攻击。影响范围涵盖所有运行 RPC portmapper 服务的 Unix/Linux 系统及网络设备。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0632"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:45.710","remediation":"在防火墙或边界设备上禁用 TCP/UDP 135 端口（RPC 端口映射器）及 137-139、445 等 SMB/RPC 相关端口的入站访问，仅允许受信任内网主机连接；通过组策略关闭不必要的 RPC 服务并将 Portmapper 绑定限制为 localhost；安装微软对应安全更新补丁，启用 Windows Firewall 默认阻止规则以降低被未授权主机枚举和利用的风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0632","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1ef693821096ed2e21366dae590c013e3dc540aa/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0632.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0632","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/32348f9346a59ffe42d1530710879fd8da26d51a/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0632.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0632.md","https://github.com/packetchaos/navi/blob/48d4e8df93f0f87e8654f6bfb01844b5dea4ed58/Queries.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/rpc_portmap.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1ef90eac7bb1a353721fe038daf41872bdff01c4/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5626-39p4-q29v/GHSA-5626-39p4-q29v.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cc528fa33408da88ea19cf3d01d2185cd0ffe95a/SSVC/data/1999/CVE-1999-0632.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/chihsuan/search-engine/blob/9dcdd3e644469883f53565740f0ba8ff617c5120/Data/E99D88C1-C798-40D7-BB8C-47E6405B9469.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0939.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0937","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0937.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0631","title":"NFS 服务未授权访问配置问题","description":"该漏洞为已被撤销的 CVE 编号，原指 NFS（网络文件系统）服务在目标主机上处于运行状态。NFS 服务默认监听 TCP/UDP 2049 端口，若未配置严格的访问控制策略（如 exports 权限限制、IP 过滤、认证机制），远程未授权攻击者可通过网络探测到该服务，进而可能尝试挂载或访问导出的文件系统，导致敏感文件泄露或进一步渗透。该问题不属于安全漏洞范畴，已被转移至通用配置枚举（CCE）进行管理，CVSS 评分 0.0，不涉及具体的攻击利用链路或需修复的软件缺陷。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0631"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.713","remediation":"如非业务需要，应在不需要 NFS 共享的服务器上关闭 NFS 服务（systemctl disable nfs-server）；确需使用时，应限制 exports 仅允许特定 IP 段访问并使用 root_squash 选项，同时在防火墙中限制 2049/TCP 端口仅对受信来源开放，推荐启用 NFSv4 及以上版本并禁用 NFSv2/v3","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0631.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0631","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0631.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0631.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0631.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0937.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0933","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0933.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0630","title":"Microsoft Windows 2000/NT NT Alerter 服务权限提升漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 与 Windows 2000 系统中默认运行 NT Alerter（警报器）与 Messenger（信使）服务，二者用于在局域网内发送弹出式管理警报与消息，且无需身份认证即可被远程或本地调用。攻击者在已获取较低权限的本地或网络账户后，可利用这些服务将特制消息发送给目标主机，借助服务以较高权限上下文执行相关操作，从而实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响启用上述服务的 Windows NT/2000 主机，攻击条件为攻击者需先获得目标系统的有效登录凭据或局域网络访问权限，利用方式是通过调用 Alerter/Messenger 服务的接口发送恶意消息以绕过正常权限限制。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0630"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:45.567","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 针对 Windows NT 4.0 和 Windows 2000 发布的安全补丁 KB189271，并将 Alerter 和 Messenger 服务启动类型设置为\"已禁用\"；若业务必需，可在组策略中通过\"网络安全：LanMan 身份验证级别\"限制远程访问，或关闭 TCP 139、445 端口阻止 net send 消息传递。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q189/2/71.asp","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1ef693821096ed2e21366dae590c013e3dc540aa/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0630.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0630","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0630.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/6d3a932c05085f06507d23e5a0893fa8fe64ce42/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0630.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1ef90eac7bb1a353721fe038daf41872bdff01c4/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vrmc-8g42-jfcf/GHSA-vrmc-8g42-jfcf.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/S/smb_svc_alerter.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0630.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/smb_svc_messenger.nasl","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--b10d3823-9a42-4e49-90e2-4307b6b967bb.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0933.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0932","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0932.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0629","title":"UNIX系统 identd服务 信息泄露漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0629 涉及主机 ident/identd 服务的安全配置问题。ident 协议（RFC 1413）允许远程主机查询本地 TCP 连接所对应的系统用户身份。当目标系统运行了 identd 服务且未做适当限制时，攻击者可通过发起本地或远程 TCP 连接并向 ident 端口（113）发起查询，获取与目标连接关联的本地用户名信息。该信息可能被用于用户身份枚举，进而为本地权限提升或针对性攻击（如猜测用户密码、利用用户级漏洞）提供辅助条件。此问题主要影响启用了 identd 服务的类 Unix 系统，攻击前提是对方开放 ident 服务且防火墙未拦截 113 端口，其本身并非可直接利用的代码执行漏洞，而是信息泄露类隐患。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0629"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:45.460","remediation":"在 Linux 系统中执行 `systemctl disable --now identd` 或注释掉 /etc/inetd.conf 中的 auth 行后重启 inetd；若业务必须保留，则通过防火墙仅允许受信任内网 IP 访问 113 端口，禁止外部网络访问该服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0629","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0629.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1ef693821096ed2e21366dae590c013e3dc540aa/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0629.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0629","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/6d3a932c05085f06507d23e5a0893fa8fe64ce42/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0629.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0629.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1ef90eac7bb1a353721fe038daf41872bdff01c4/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r25p-h4hw-w7gf/GHSA-r25p-h4hw-w7gf.json","https://github.com/JakeVincet/nvt/blob/f39b9cba98d614dd2a567b15cce1a5eeb97ad782/auth_enabled.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0629.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/entrysky/mageni/blob/c58dcc9bc43b7fb267bb10a8083ada356fbc81d1/plugins/2020/linux/gb_ident_inf_disc_vuln.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0932.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0918","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0918.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0625","title":"Unix rpc.rquotad 远程配额服务配置安全隐患漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0625 描述的是主机上 rpc.rquotad 远程磁盘配额守护进程服务处于运行状态的安全配置问题。rpc.rquotad 是 Unix/Linux 系统上用于 NFS 网络文件系统远程磁盘配额管理的 RPC 服务，该协议设计年代较早，未对远程请求实施严格的身份认证与访问控制。当系统启用该服务并使其处于运行状态时，未经身份验证的远程攻击者可通过网络向目标主机的 rpc.rquotad 端口发送特制 RPC 请求，获取系统用户的磁盘配额信息，甚至在某些条件下利用该服务进行本地权限提升或作为后续攻击的跳板。该漏洞本质上属于安全配置缺陷而非软件代码漏洞，NVD 将其 CVSS 评分设为 0.0 分（严重级别 LOW）。受影响范围主要为启用了 NFS 服务的 Unix/Linux 主机，攻击者无需事先认证即可在低复杂度条件下完成利用。根据 NVD 评估建议，rpc.rquotad 是一种不安全且已过时的协议，用户应禁用该服务或阻止相关 RPC 端口的网络访问以消除风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0625"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:44.947","remediation":"建议在不需要磁盘配额服务的系统上停止并禁用 rpc.rquotad 服务（如执行 `chkconfig rpc.rquotad off` 并 `kill` 相关进程），或通过防火墙/主机策略限制 111 及 1022 等 RPC 端口仅对受信任内网开放，升级到已默认关闭该服务的 Linux 发行版最新补丁版本（如 RHEL/CentOS 更新 nfs-utils 至厂商最新版）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0625","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4d7236390d3d65194e590e3c8620543620af3984/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0625.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0625","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0625.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/6d3a932c05085f06507d23e5a0893fa8fe64ce42/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0625.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1ef90eac7bb1a353721fe038daf41872bdff01c4/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r8qg-5ffw-4wgf/GHSA-r8qg-5ffw-4wgf.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0625.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/rpc_rquotad.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83127/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0918.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0916","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0916.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0624","title":"SunOS rstat 服务特权提升漏洞","description":"rstat/rstatd 远程统计服务存在权限提升漏洞，该服务在 Unix/Linux 系统中用于远程监控系统性能统计信息（如 CPU 负载、内存使用、磁盘 I/O 等）。攻击者可利用该服务配置不当或权限配置不当的缺陷，通过滥用 rstatd 服务的特权操作获取系统敏感信息或提升权限。该漏洞影响运行 rstatd 服务的 Unix/Linux 系统（如 SunOS、Solaris、Linux 等），攻击者无需认证即可远程访问该服务获取系统敏感统计信息，配合其他漏洞可进一步提升权限至 root 权限。建议禁用不必要的 rstatd 服务或配置严格的访问控制列表限制访问来源。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0624"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:44.800","remediation":"建议禁用或卸载系统中不必要的 rstat/rstatd（rstatd 守护进程），通过修改 /etc/inetd.conf 或 systemd 服务配置注释掉 rstatd 相关条目并重启服务，同时使用防火墙限制 772/773/775 等 rpc.rstatd 端口仅允许受信任内网访问，以杜绝该服务暴露带来的信息泄露与权限提升风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0624","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0624.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a23c9152c0ce51f4625e88e1e6abe715ca2d7579/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0624.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0624","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/6d3a932c05085f06507d23e5a0893fa8fe64ce42/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0624.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0624.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1ef90eac7bb1a353721fe038daf41872bdff01c4/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-44f4-mv9h-2724/GHSA-44f4-mv9h-2724.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/2011/secpod_rpc_rstatd_udp.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0624.json","https://github.com/LubyRuffy/plugins/blob/f873b19f27c95eaf2993ca4acde5cb7965d2ee3f/2011/secpod_rpc_rstatd_tcp.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83127/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0916.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0915","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0915.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0623","title":"X.Org X Window System 服务配置不当","description":"CVE-1999-0623 已被 NVD 官方拒绝使用，原因为该候选编号描述的是一个系统配置检查项（X Window 服务正在运行），而非直接构成安全漏洞的缺陷。此类配置检测更适合归入通用配置枚举（CCE）体系管理，不应作为漏洞编号使用。该条目无 CVSS 评分，无有效影响范围与攻击条件说明。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0623"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.640","remediation":"若无需图形界面或远程 X11 功能，建议关闭 X Window 服务（如 Linux 下执行 `systemctl stop gdm` 并禁用开机启动）。如需使用 X11 转发，应限制仅监听 127.0.0.1，并通过 SSH 隧道（`ssh -X`）安全转发，避免将 TCP 端口 6000 暴露到外部网络。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0623.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0623","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0623.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0623.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0623.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0915.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0914","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0914.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0622","title":"通用 DNS 服务配置检测（非安全漏洞）","description":"CVE-1999-0622 已被正式驳回（REJECT），原候选编号描述为\"DNS 相关服务组件正在运行\"。该条目仅涉及系统配置层面的 DNS 服务开放状态，属于安全配置审计范畴而非可直接利用的安全漏洞，不存在攻击路径与利用条件。此类配置信息更适合在通用配置枚举（CCE）中覆盖，不适用作 CVE 漏洞编号。因此该 CVE 不具有实际漏洞意义，不记录 CVSS 评分。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0622"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.607","remediation":"配置 DNS 服务时应限制区域传输仅允许授权的辅助 DNS 服务器，关闭递归查询或将其限制为仅内网客户端，防止 DNS 反射放大攻击。同时部署 DNSSEC 保障数据完整性，禁止版本信息泄露，并定期审计 DNS 日志。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0622.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0622","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0622.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0622.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blo